These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, fantasy, mystery
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, r&b, salsa, techno
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, indonesian, polish
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, may, august, march
1. the colombian is the fan of techno##1
2. the indonesian is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
3. the colombian is the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is the person watching fantasy movies##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
8. the canadian is on the far right##1
9. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | mystery   | adventure  | fantasy  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | techno    | metal      | salsa    |
| Nationality   | polish | colombian | indonesian | canadian |
| Birthday     | march  | october       | may    | august     |

