.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, mirinda, sprite
There 4 different types of food: corn, nectarine, onion, plum
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, hiking, photography, woodworking
4 different games are played: whist, go, billiard, monopoly
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 2. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 4. the person eating corn is the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 7. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is between the person eating corn and the person eating onion##2
 9. the person eating plum is on the right of the person playing go##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person eating corn and the person eating onion##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | mirinda    | sprite      | hot-chocolate |
| Food       | corn        | plum       | onion       | nectarine     |
| Hobby      | photography | filmmaking | woodworking | hiking        |
| Game        | go       | monopoly     | billiard         | whist           |

