 3. the person eating kale is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 4. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
 5. the blend-smoker is between the fonseca-smoker and the baccarat-smoker##2
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is the person eating cucumber##1
 8. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
 9. the baccarat-smoker is the person driving the train##1
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
