5. the person eating apricot is the person driving the subway##1
6. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
7. the musician is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
8. the designer is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
9. the electrician is on the right of the designer##1

.:: Answer ::.
